18 (C) AN EMPLOYEE MAY USE UP TO 15 DAYS OF DISASTER SERVICE LEAVE IN
19 ANY 12–MONTH PERIOD ONLY AFTER OBTAINING APPROVAL FROM THE EMPLOYEE’S
20 GOVERNMENTAL UNIT.
21 (D) DURING A PROLONGED OR RECURRENT DISASTER, THE EMPLOYEE’S
22 GOVERNMENTAL UNIT MAY:
